00:56:16.290 --> 00:56:19.732
thank god I have a
program of recovery

00:56:19.732 --> 00:56:20.690
now, including therapy.

00:56:20.690 --> 00:56:22.500
When I start talking about
this program of recovery,

00:56:22.500 --> 00:56:23.160
what does that look like?

