I'm part of the 12
step fellowship.

00:56:24.630 --> 00:56:26.190
I also do therapy.

00:56:26.190 --> 00:56:27.990
I do meditation.

00:56:27.990 --> 00:56:29.670
I make sure that I
work out, do yoga,

00:56:29.670 --> 00:56:32.430
all of the different things.

00:56:32.430 --> 00:56:35.520
Of service to others as much
