00:56:35.520 --> 00:56:37.106
of spiritual connection.

00:56:40.230 --> 00:56:43.650
Because of that, I've
been able to deal

00:56:43.650 --> 00:56:48.150
with the issues of my
parents both passing while I

00:56:48.150 --> 00:56:50.910
was in active addiction.

00:56:50.910 --> 00:57:01.400
As far as how it's changed
or affected me as a parent,

00:57:01.400 --> 00:57:08.050
I make sure that my daughter--

00:57:08.050 --> 00:57:15.670
she's very sensitive as it
is, anyway, but I've never

00:57:15.670 --> 00:57:17.688
raised my voice at her.

00:57:17.688 --> 00:57:19.480
I mean, luckily she's
