Well, you don't trust me?

01:00:02.370 --> 01:00:04.860
No, this is just
something that we do.

01:00:04.860 --> 01:00:05.630
So yeah.

01:00:05.630 --> 01:00:07.088
There are a lot of
different things

01:00:07.088 --> 01:00:13.250
that my addiction, and
more so my recovery,

01:00:13.250 --> 01:00:15.560
has done to sort of
inform me of the decisions

