If you can go out there and
smoke crack on the weekend

01:12:50.060 --> 01:12:52.700
and come back and be a
beautiful, loving, supporting

01:12:52.700 --> 01:12:55.495
human being that is involved
in society, I don't care.

01:12:55.495 --> 01:12:56.870
I don't have a
problem with that.

01:12:59.580 --> 01:13:01.290
Same with weed
being legal or not.

01:13:01.290 --> 01:13:03.550
I prefer it being legal.

01:13:03.550 --> 01:13:06.510
It's regulated, it's
taxed, it pays some bills,

01:13:06.510 --> 01:13:08.160
all the rest of that.

01:13:08.160 --> 01:13:10.200
For people who are not
like me, who are not

01:13:10.200 --> 01:13:12.330
addicts, who have
the ability to handle

01:13:12.330 --> 01:13:14.890
it just like a glass of
wine every once in a while.

01:13:14.890 --> 01:13:19.380
Look, addiction is
defined as the inability

01:13:19.380 --> 01:13:23.910
to stop a behavior despite
negative consequences.

01:13:23.910 --> 01:13:26.760
A negative behavior that
you cannot stop that you are

01:13:26.760 --> 01:13:30.390
compulsively continuing to
engage in despite negative

01:13:30.390 --> 01:13:31.157
behaviors.

01:13:31.157 --> 01:13:33.240
If you're engaging in a
behavior and there are not

01:13:33.240 --> 01:13:35.930
the negative consequences,
it's not an addiction.

01:13:35.930 --> 01:13:36.480
So cool.

01:13:39.140 --> 01:13:39.860
That's my answer.

01:13:41.523 --> 01:13:42.940
CAROLINE DEHNERT
MOYER: All right.

01:13:42.940 --> 01:13:44.937
Like all good joint
Al-Anon AA meetings,

01:13:44.937 --> 01:13:47.020
we're going to end with
the serenity prayer, which

01:13:47.020 --> 01:13:48.510
I actually had to write down.

01:13:48.510 --> 01:13:49.420
JAM ALKER: I got it memorized.

01:13:49.420 --> 01:13:51.337
CAROLINE DEHNERT MOYER:
He's got it memorized.

01:13:51.337 --> 01:13:53.650
If anybody knows it,
please speak it with us.

01:13:53.650 --> 01:13:58.930
So God grant me the serenity
to accept the things I cannot

01:13:58.930 --> 01:14:02.540
change, the courage to
change the things I can,

01:14:02.540 --> 01:14:06.250
and the wisdom to
know the difference.

01:14:06.250 --> 01:14:06.850
Thanks

01:14:06.850 --> 01:14:11.383
[APPLAUSE]

01:14:11.383 --> 01:14:12.550
JAM ALKER: Thanks, you guys.

01:14:12.550 --> 01:14:14.400
Thank you.

